      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there’s no way out of it. like, i've tried every \"resilience\" thing and \"growth mindset\" thing people tell you in grad school, but it’s just more work. more effort. i'm just so drained. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the pressure is to just... stop everything. to just find some actual peace.",
